All:
With Amazon Pay, we make it simple for the hundreds of millions of Amazon customers worldwide to easily log in and purchase from your store using information already stored their Amazon account. With easy setup in Magento 2.2.4, Amazon Pay provides your customers with a trusted and familiar checkout experience.
